<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><span lang="HE" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">שלום רב,</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><span lang="HE" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">בהמשך לשיחתנו, את </span><span lang="HE" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">הטפסים </font></span><span lang="HE" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">ניתן להעביר לידנו </span>באמצעות <span style="font-size: 12pt;">העלאתם לקישור זה:</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><font face="arial"><u>{!Case.formtitan_ivf_upload_files_female__c}</u></font><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="HE" style="line-height: 22px;">או באמצעות פקס שמספרו&nbsp;</span>{!Case.Fax_Number_IVF__c}.&nbsp;</font></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="HE" style="line-height: 22px;"><br></span></font></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><font face="arial">הטפסים שיש להעביר לידנו:&nbsp;</font></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><font face="arial">1.<span style="white-space:pre">	</span>מסמך ההחלטה עם סימון ההחלטה</font></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><font style="" face="arial"><span lang="HE" style="line-height: 22px;"></span></font></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><font face="arial">2.<span style="white-space:pre">	</span><b>צילום תעודת זהות עם חתימה וציון התאריך על גבי הצילום</b></font></p><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: right;"><br></div><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; unicode-bidi: embed;" dir="RTL"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="HE" style="line-height: 22px;">לכל שאלה ועניין ניתן לשלוח מייל לכתובת&nbsp;</span><span lang="HE" style="line-height: 24px;">{!Case.Site_Email__c}.</span></font></p><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span lang="HE" style="line-height: 24px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><br></span></font></span></div><p dir="RTL" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; unicode-bidi: embed;"><span lang="HE" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">בברכה,</span></p><p dir="RTL" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: right; unicode-bidi: embed;"><span lang="HE" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">אסותא מרכזים רפואיים</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>